{"tid":1374050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈 729係死線 730全民罷工","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:34.000Z","uid":176460,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a74dd79cfd640e917c7ab45afb8855ec1e22ad5b","tid":1374050,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"港鐵車長已經公開講左呢兩個日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/photos/a.224908467685595/1267256670117431/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThingsAtHongKong%2Fphotos%2Fa.224908467685595%2F1267256670117431%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F1wmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=f1a53bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/photos/a.224908467685595/1267256670117431/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你好驚冇左份工，果日你可以名正言順咁話冇車撘返唔到工<br />\n<br />\n連港鐵都做到o既時候，你仲有咩理由唔做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，爭氣一次</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">729死線 730罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n文宣組麻煩煲大佢！！"},{"pid":"f032368fdb701d43a6cd048d385a0fc72f21a545","tid":1374050,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a201cbc6d49e9418df320d5bfe84bca2021c2b2","tid":1374050,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"424958bacc87c541464b26e1a8794007051e947d","tid":1374050,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6e6fe098e6d1a4d6404c36cec6f974c6e7c651","tid":1374050,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T